	(text_box "JX* and JS* are soldered horizontally at the corresponding PCB edge, with JS* serving as stabilizers.\n\nJB* and JH* are soldered normally and serve as the receptacles for the corresponding JX* and JS*.\n\nPlease freely decide which ones use male 2xN headers and which ones use female 2xN headers."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
